            "behavior": "B4",
            "status": "ready",
            "evidence": "app/src/domain/adjudication/adjudicator.ts:27-34 (AdjudicateLineResult type) includes all required fields: reasons[], explanation (string with numbers), payableCents, memberResponsibilityCents. Persisted at adjudication.repository.ts:10-20 (NewAdjudication type) and schema.ts:99-120 with explanation column storing the breakdown text."
