          }
        ],
        "gaps": [
          {
            "item": "B1 happy-path state transition validation (SUBMITTED → APPROVED for 1-line claim)",
            "file": "app/src/domain/state-machines/claim-state.ts",
            "what": "aggregateClaimStatus(lines: LineOutcome[]) at line 19 validates: single line with status=APPROVED and reasons=[APPROVED] (no LIMIT_EXCEEDED) → returns APPROVED. Transition: claim.service.ts:62-68 sets SUBMITTED, then line 192-199 sets claim status to APPROVED after aggregation. Exact chain: (1) claim created SUBMITTED null→SUBMITTED (line 62-68), (2) line created PENDING null→PENDING (line 80-86), (3) line adjudicated to APPROVED (line 125), setStatus PENDING→APPROVED (line 133-139), (4) outcomes=[{status:APPROVED, reasons:[APPROVED]}] passed to aggregateClaimStatus (line 192), returns APPROVED, setStatus SUBMITTED→APPROVED (line 193-199).",
