            "file": "app/src/routes/claims.routes.ts",
            "what": "Stub only (1-line comment header). Implement GET handler: (1) fetch claim by ID, (2) fetch all adjudications (payable sums), (3) return {claimId, status, totalPayableCents, totalMemberResponsibilityCents}. Status comes from status_transitions table current state; payables sum from adjudications.payable_cents grouped by line.",
